                   <p class="mb-1" style="box-sizing: border-box;margin-top: 0;margin-bottom: .25rem!important;">2. You may file a new certificate at any time if the number of your exemptions
                      <b style="box-sizing: border-box;font-weight: bolder;"><i style="box-sizing: border-box;">increases</i></b>.</p>
