                         own exemption on a separate certificate.</p>
                      <p class="mb-1" style="box-sizing: border-box;margin-top: 0;margin-bottom: .25rem!important;">(b) The support of a dependent for whom you claimed exemption
                         is taken over by someone else.</p>
                      <p class="mb-3" style="box-sizing: border-box;margin-top: 0;margin-bottom: 1rem!important;">(c) You find that a dependent for whom you claimed exemption
                         must be dropped for federal purposes.</p>
